{
  "stem": "22391.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then somebody who was there already for a long time, they said, throw me the coat because you're not going to have it anyhow.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they're taking everything away from you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you know, I didn't realize that is true.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I hold onto my mother's fur coat until the last minute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we had to walk through Mengele's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, Mengele's was the one you go right or you go left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where it happened-- I went to one side and I was looking for my mother, but I had never come across with, with her or even anybody else.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, at night, when we were there the first night and the girls were telling us who was there already for a long time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was crying, looking for my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she said, why are you looking for your mother?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see the flame over there and the smoke?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's where your mother is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the end of the-- Did you believe her?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That you don't want to believe anything because you think that telling your stories about then-- as days went by, you suddenly realize when you saw that things really was happening and that was the true story.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they put us into a, a room that we must have been 50 girls sleeping on the floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no roof or anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If somebody had to go to the bathroom, which was no bathroom-- it was like an [? awning ?] little thing-- they went to on you because there was no way to get out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's all that it was, so-- it was-- I should stop, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
